  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Community-Acquired Pneumonia has become common. Additionally, the mortality is high. But the
      epidemiology of pathogen is various in different areas, which is crucial for the key
      treatment. In addition, the risk factors of patients who died in 3 or 7 days in china is not
      clear, comparing with patients who died in 14 or 28 days or who survived.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
